<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Mint</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: #f4f4f5;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      }
      .wrapper {
        max-width: 560px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      .header {
        background: #18181b;
        padding: 28px 32px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: -0.3px;
      }
      .body {
        padding: 32px;
      }
      .body h2 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        color: #18181b;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .body p {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        color: #3f3f46;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .features {
        margin: 24px 0;
        border: 1px solid #e4e4e7;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .feature {
        display: flex;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #f4f4f5;
      }
      .feature:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }
      .feature-icon {
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
        background: #18181b;
        border-radius: 6px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin-right: 14px;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 32px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .feature-text strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #18181b;
        margin-bottom: 2px;
      }
      .feature-text span {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #71717a;
      }
      .footer {
        padding: 20px 32px;
        border-top: 1px solid #f4f4f5;
      }
      .footer p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #a1a1aa;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Mint</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <h2>Welcome to Mint, {{ name }}!</h2>
        <p>Your account is ready. Here's what you can do with Mint:</p>
        <div class="features">
          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">💳</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Send &amp; Receive Money</strong>
              <span>Transfer funds instantly to anyone on Mint.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Track Your Spending</strong>
              <span>Automatic categorization and monthly insights.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Set Budgets</strong>
              <span>Get alerts before you overspend in any category.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>
          Verify your email to unlock full access and start using your wallet.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          &copy; 2026 Mint. You're receiving this because you signed up for a
          Mint account.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
